replies.body:
Well i quit the game for a bit in an attempt to become a pro fortnite player ;) i did get pretty good but eventually summer ended and i couldnt no life the game like the rest of the kids playing so i got caught up skill wise and missed all the changing metas, then i got back into stratus and here i am :D

Education wise i finished my exams and now am in college revising for even more exams

Hope ur life has been good too <3

replies.body: College aye? I finished my college apps a couple months ago and waiting another two months to get my responses from them. I am hoping for the best, there's two I really want to go because the beach is literally your backyard because the campus is located on a beach. Other than that, my social life has been ok, not the greatest or like how it used to be in the past. I just been working a lot of hours at my job and school; if I do get to do something else, I usually watch youtube, listen to music, or play overwatch lol.
